author: pburba
msg: Follow-up to rev 15466 (propsets of non-svn:* props).
The ebcdic port interprets all props, even non-svn:* ones, set on the
command line as utf-8.  So when getting non-svn:* propvals attempt to convert
them to something human readable (i.e. ebcdic) if it seems appropriate
(i.e. the propval is valid utf-8).
* subversion/clients/cmdline/propget-cmd.c
(svn_cl__propget): Convert utf-8 non-svn:* propvals to ebcdic.
